<html t:type="layout" title="Index | release02"
      xmlns:t="http://tapestry.apache.org/schema/tapestry_5_4.xsd">

<!-- Most of the page content, including <head>, <body>, etc. tags, comes from Layout.tml -->

<!-- Main hero unit for a primary marketing message or call to action -->
<div class="row">
    <div class="col-6">
        <p>
            <img src="${asset:context:images/logo_7add5486.png}" alt="${message:greeting}" title="${message:greeting}" width="174"/>
        </p>
        <h1 id="title">${message:greeting}</h1>
        <p>The current time is: <strong>${currentTime}</strong></p>
        <p>Current project state: <strong>experimental</strong></p>
        <p>
            It is a simple sales manager workstation interface that can retrieve product stock balances 
            from a database in a simple form, convert them into a pivot table with dynamic stock columns 
            whose composition depends on the data source. 
        </p>
        <p>    
            Document attributes Company, Partner and linked contract can be selected from the respective lists.
            Product quantity could be selected by pressing quantity in the respective column.
         </p>
         <p>   
            On pressing Print invoice document attributes are send to the server. Server sends back a pdf file,
            which can be saved and opened on the client. 
        </p>
    </div>
</div>


<div class="row">
    <div class="col-6">
         <p><t:eventlink event="complete" class="btn btn-primary">Open sales manager workplace &raquo;</t:eventlink></p>
    </div>
</div>

</html>
